                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2024-56433\nSeverity: low\nPackage: passwd\nVersion: 1:4.17.4-2\nFix Version: \nType: deb\nLocation: /var/lib/dpkg/status\nData Namespace: debian:distro:debian:13\nLink: [CVE-2024-56433](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2024-56433)",
